<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.2.3">
<l>aṇṭa rāṉavar vāṉavar kōṉukkeṉ ṟamaittacō ṟatuvellām</l>
<l>uṇṭu kōnirai mēyttavai kāttava ṉukantiṉi tuṟaikōyil</l>
<l>koṇṭa lārmuḻa viṟkuḷir vārpoḻil kulamayil naṭamāṭa</l>
<l>vaṇṭu tāṉicai pāṭiṭu nāṅkūr vaṇpuru ṭōttamamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where dwells sweetly rejoicing the one who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having eaten all the rice that the guards and herders</l>
<l>Made for the celestials’ king, [and] having grazed the cowherd,</l>
<l rend="indent">protected them,</l>
<l>Is Vaṉpuruṭōttamam in Nānkūr where bees boldly sing the music,</l>
<l>As flocks of peacocks perform a dance in a wide, cool grove</l>
<l rend="indent">where clouds rumble like drums.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
